.3</span> Lepton</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">References:</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">λεπτόν</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(lepton)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:42\">MRK 12:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:59\">LUK 12:59</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:2\">LUK 21:2</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">See the comments under <em>kodrantēs</em> above, <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">11.6.2.2 Kodrantes&lt;REALIA:11.6.2.2&gt;</a>.</h2>\n</div>",
